c: 9
v: 3
t: "A declaration from God and His Messenger ňĻis madeňļ to all people on the day of the greater pilgrimage¬†that God and His Messenger are free of the polytheists. So if you ňĻpagansňļ repent, it will be better for you. But if you turn away, then know that you will have no escape from God. And give good news ňĻO Prophetňļ to the disbelievers of a painful punishment"